The Brotherhood F-2 "Hellkitten", with a 108HP engine capable of reaching over 180km/h, 2,500m flight ceiling, with two 7.62x54mm machineguns for offense and a smaller 3mm machinegun for defense, as well as a railing to install ordinance like grenade casings or other future explosives and a 300km operations range. This aircraft has surpassed the previous airframe by a significant margin. This feat of engineering was only possible thanks to the most brilliant minds of Kameri and a generous investment fund from all Wright B. Co. partners.

kinhou01/03/24
The SSSK has finished work on its new Brotherhood warplane, with powerful armament of two .30-cal and one .50-cal. machine guns. The plane is capable of carrying 200 lbs. of bombs or a single torpedo. It contains the most sophisticated radio systems with different frequencies for wing-sized communication and strategic level orders. Fitted with secret systems to detect enemy craft and even ground vehicles from certain distances, and with an impressive speed of over 370km/h, an effective range of 440km, and a ceiling of 4,800m, this aircraft is, without a doubt, the best on the planet. The F-3 "Ghost"
